title: 383D.61 COMPREHENSIVE PLAN.
text: Notwithstanding any provision of section 394.23 to the contrary, the Board of County Commissioners of the county of Dakota may prepare a comprehensive plan for the orderly future physical development of any area of the county or parts thereof. The plan, which may include text and maps, shall be approved and certified by the board and when so certified by the board shall be referred to as the comprehensive plan. The plan may thereafter be amended or added to by the board.
